data.value:
We are a VoluntaRO and we want to bring sport lovers together!
WHAT(The Solution): A community app connecting volunteers and events. We create a sustainable volunteers’ program that will motivate and bring together people of all ages, genders, races, nationalities and religions and develop youth leaders.
HOW (Vision): By sharing the values of sports (sports being the only activity out there that brings people together). Motivating as many individuals as possible to serve for its community for a healthier society.
WHY (MISSION): The volunteer culture is not developed in sport, at the moment. Now you have the chance to meet all your favourite athletes and help them and enjoy new experiences!
